{"tid":338450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CIA局長﹕最大安全挑戰來自中國","createTime":"2017-07-28T08:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T09:05:08.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbd9f3d8d20850dd6d1316e96e3e61f53c1afe3","tid":338450,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">CIA局長﹕最大安全挑戰來自中國</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170728/s00053/41d77136b4f18ed1b1758882a22e8de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170728%2Fs00053%2F41d77136b4f18ed1b1758882a22e8de2.jpg&h=52f8563e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國中情局（CIA）局長蓬佩奧昨在1月上任後的首次受訪中說，長遠來看，對美國最大的安全挑戰來自中國，而非俄羅斯。另外，美國海軍太平洋艦隊司令斯威夫特上將表示，若美國總統特朗普下令向中國發動核攻擊，他將會執行命令。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo，圖）接受「華盛頓自由燈塔」網（Washington Free Beacon）訪問時表示，中國、俄羅斯和伊朗都將在未來對美國造成重大問題，但擁有良好經濟和軍事實力不斷增強的中國是更大的威脅，「中長期來看，中國有能力成為美國最大的對手」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又說，中國大舉收購美國科技企業，「如果你仔細觀察，他們或許要麼試圖竊取我們的東西，要麼確保可以打敗我們，而且通常是兩者兼有之」。<br />\n<br />\n軍方﹕倘總統下令 會對華核攻擊<br />\n<br />\n另據美聯社報道，斯威夫特（Scott Swift）27日出席澳洲國立大學一個安全會議時，被問到若特朗普下令向中國發動核攻擊，會否執行，他稱「答案是肯定的」。事後，太平洋艦隊發言人布朗（Charlie Brown）為事件降溫，稱斯威夫特只想表達文人政府控制軍隊的原則，即軍隊要服從總統，形容該問題是「荒謬的假設」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170728/s00013/1501177741939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170728%2Fs00013%2F1501177741939&d=HKPVGitP8a%2FZKOo55vTIzm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=637ecec5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170728%2Fs00013%2F1501177741939&h=89394ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170728/s00013/1501177741939</a>"},{"pid":"1e4885202dbdd27d17b3bc1154c9a4d19dca85f4","tid":338450,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81b07e26ee7e008172d1faf4c5b80d1222f14a2","tid":338450,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"Charlie Brown from peanut?"},{"pid":"bfe9dffd87c1b5a45f84342d355eabb102606882","tid":338450,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}